LGTM, but I was going the other direction: a custom `GomegaStringer` that could do something like
```
    s := array[0] + "\n...\n"
    previous := array[0]
    for [rest of lines] {
        if line != previous+1 {
            s += "unexpected: line\n"
        }
        previous = line
    }
    s += "last line\n"
```
...just to save human eyes. But yours sure is quicker.
